data.title: Jane Wall
data.meta_description: Jane Wall. Actress: Ghost Whisperer - Stimmen aus dem Jenseits. Television, film and theatre actress best known for her 4 seasons on Bafta award winning drama, "The Bill". British/Nigerian actress raised in London, United Kingdom. Jane trained at Mountview Theatre School and The School of the Science of Acting. Jane lives in Los Angeles with her husband and 2 children.
